{"tid":1357314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵職員：你班人喺到不合作有咩用","createTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T16:53:25.000Z","uid":275109,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2ef9c5d2adbb61820c857f0f1d3b141801f63b","tid":1357314,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有用！每一件事都有佢嘅價值！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要達到每一個成功，都必然會經歷艱辛和喜悅：<br />\n但請緊記鬥奮過後才是勝利。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KmaFuAP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKmaFuAP.png&h=6ed8936f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想當年甘地發起世界歷史上第一個全國性的非暴力反抗運動，又稱<span style=\"color: orange;\">非暴力</span>不合作運動。<br />\n甘地呼籲以非暴力的不合作手段（例如：不納稅、不入公立學校、不入公職，並多次絕食），抵制英國的統治。<br />\n運動使當地的殖民政府近乎<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">癱瘓</span></span>，迫使英國政府不得不頒布新憲法，讓印度逐漸發展自治體制。<br />\n<br />\nSource: Wikipedia"},{"pid":"178c5c426fe563497792c62c43ab9ec43c52ce7b","tid":1357314,"uid":275109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:42:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日 7:30 一齊金鐘塔鐵</span>"},{"pid":"6a23dbc001d650ee23631746de5c76c9b2ff7e93","tid":1357314,"uid":275109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:43:20.000Z","msg":"Sor頭先開台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2099c0cd0a846026f3039c67fe500d7a8a7b1ab9","tid":1357314,"uid":276215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb247880b5bd55a4a9154216b2bb11f971cfb08f","tid":1357314,"uid":115264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:49:21.